{
  "stem": "25773.7",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all the young people able who could run away by trains to the Russian-occupied part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was Russia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were not afraid to be exterminated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They went there to-- many of them perished on the way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Many of them got ill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Many of them got lost and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Those who came-- went first-- my husband ran to Lviv, because his parents were in Lviv, and he already worked in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My sister ran to-- to with friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She ran to-- She ran to-- to-- to-- first to Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Bialystok was on the border between Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then through various stories, which I hope she will recall herself, various, various stories, through the forest, and through the people who guided them, to giving them money, all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Encountered-- encountering Russian police who wanted to shoot them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Arrived in Kovno, Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Lithuania at that time was already under Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And shortly afterwards, the Germans re-entered Lithuania from the ghetto, and liquidated all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there's the famous book, there is a Kovno-- there is a ghetto story of Kovno, of Lithuania, even performed in the-- in the-- in the theater.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were very nervous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were refugees.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they said, they don't want to stay in Russia-- in Kovno, in Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They want to first-- they didn't know how.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And by extremely lucky chance, there was the firm, you know, the firm called Phillips, a Dutch firm.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "A young man who worked there-- and word got round-- I couldn't say that exactly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But the word got around, even Dr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Martin Gilbert writes about it in his book of Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The-- they-- they-- I suddenly don't remember what I was saying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was-- yes, and it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
